ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: it is a group led discussion class where is speak about the work we have been doing on our dissertation, qualifying exam, recent grants, etc.
This is a very helpful course while working on the dissertation proposal and I would highly recommend this course to another student during this phase of doctoral work.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: this course helped me to understand different areas of research me fellow colleagues are working on
I was able to refine my dissertation proposal through feedback from other students in the course.
